# AI File Upload System

The platform now supports scientific material uploads.

---

## Supported File Types

The current version supports:

```text
PDF
DOCX
TXT
```

---

## Upload Flow

The flow works as follows:

```text
Teacher/Admin uploads file
↓
Django receives file
↓
Text extraction service runs
↓
Extracted text is cleaned
↓
Text is appended to CourseAIKnowledge
↓
Original file is saved
```

---

## File Text Extraction

A dedicated extraction service was created:

```text
ai_assistant/services/file_text_extractor.py
```

The service:

- Detects file type
- Extracts text
- Cleans invalid characters
- Returns safe text

---

## PostgreSQL NUL Character Fix

During implementation, PostgreSQL raised the error:

```text
ValueError: A string literal cannot contain NUL (0x00) characters.
```

Cause:

Some uploaded files contained hidden null characters.

Solution:

A cleaning layer was added:

```python
text.replace("\x00", "")
```

before saving extracted text.

